OL,4,CGreensill row: Civil servants ordered
OL,5,Cto declare second jobs
OL,6, Government departments have been
OL,7, ordered to find out by the end of the
OL,8, week whether senior officials have
OL,9, rule-breaking second jobs.
OL,11,FCabinet Secretary Simon Case has asked
OL,12,Fcolleagues to declare paid roles or
OL,13,Foutside interests that "might conflict"
OL,14,Fwith Civil Service rules.
OL,16,FThe move comes after it emerged a top
OL,17,Fofficial joined a financial firm while
OL,18,Fstill working for the government.
OL,20,FBill Crothers says his recruitment by
OL,21,FGreensill Capital was "transparent".
